<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="pause-n">pause <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /pɔːz/    美 /pɔːz/  </p>
<p>[C]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>中断；暂停：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>without (a) pause 
不停地</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He made a short pause and then went on reading. 
他稍稍停顿了一下又继续念下去。</p></div></div>